{"tid":1161531,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"澳洲大選   保守派總理莫理森「爆冷」勝出","createTime":"2019-05-19T09:05:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-19T12:05:57.000Z","uid":20058,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"273f525c39fef538466a380c5330ac82139f976e","tid":1161531,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T09:05:31.000Z","msg":"【澳洲大選】<br />\n【保守派總理莫理森「爆冷」勝出】<br />\n<br />\n澳洲大選，總理莫理森領導的執政聯盟「爆冷」勝出。<br />\n<br />\n有澳洲政治分析員對大選結果感到意外，落敗的工黨在選前民調，甚至過往三年的支持度，均領先執政聯盟，最終卻被聯盟成功翻盤，不及莫里森集中打經濟牌奏效。<br />\n<br />\n分析指，立場保守的執政聯盟勝出，意味澳洲其他政策方向，也不會有大變動，預料將維持強硬對華立場及移民政策。<br />\n<br />\n#有線新聞 #澳洲大選 #執政聯盟 #莫理森 #經濟牌<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/186040714921338/posts/1113654672159933?s=100001313257075&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F186040714921338%2Fposts%2F1113654672159933%3Fs%3D100001313257075%26v%3De%26sfns%3Dmo&d=ywm3zvd%2FSAlFHYQsdiPdPbXqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=7b1e67cc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/186040714921338/posts/1113654672159933?s=100001313257075&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"d181c729c66885f9edb94ce4f4d90eb8fb2e2b00","tid":1161531,"uid":4783,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T09:07:41.000Z","msg":"咩爆冷姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我記得選前已經好多人講工黨個啲虛火黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc4ae00a3873905f9b01d5da5500731b4c5904d3","tid":1161531,"uid":5822,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T10:20:00.000Z","msg":"理得你咩人中 幫幫美國手就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ac7b93b5aa5afc26d602cde682279821d71667e","tid":1161531,"uid":158270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T10:34:17.000Z","msg":"Fake news fake polls"},{"pid":"38a59b39d80ba1a1f4ac735f2bee1a4f3a264a7b","tid":1161531,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":